import React from 'react';
import { ChakraProvider, Box, Grid, GridItem, Heading, Text, Input, Button, Container, Flex, FormControl, FormLabel, Image } from '@chakra-ui/react';
import { LockIcon, EmailIcon } from '@chakra-ui/icons';

const AdminLoginPage = () => {
  return (
    <ChakraProvider>
      <Box minHeight="100vh" bgGradient="linear(to-t, teal.200, teal.300)">
        {/* Header */}
        <Box py={4} color="white">
          <Container maxW="container.lg">
            <Flex alignItems="center" justifyContent="space-between">
              //<Image src="/logo.svg" alt="Logo" boxSize="50px" />
              <Heading size="lg">Admin Login</Heading>
            </Flex>
          </Container>
        </Box>
        
        {/* Main Content */}
        <Grid templateColumns="repeat(5, 1fr)" gap={4} p={4}>
          {/* Left Menu */}
          <GridItem colSpan={1} bg="white" p={4} borderRadius="md">
            <Heading size="md" mb={4}>Left Menu</Heading>
            <Box>
              <Text>Dashboard</Text>
              <Text>Seller Tool</Text>
              <Text>BuyLeads</Text>
              <Text>Settings</Text>
            </Box>
          </GridItem>

          {/* Login Form */}
          <GridItem colSpan={4} bg="white" p={8} borderRadius="md">
            <Heading size="md" mb={6}>Login</Heading>
            <FormControl>
              <FormLabel>Email Address</FormLabel>
              <Flex alignItems="center">
                <EmailIcon mr={2} />
                <Input placeholder="Enter your email" />
              </Flex>
            </FormControl>
            <FormControl mt={4}>
              <FormLabel>Password</FormLabel>
              <Flex alignItems="center">
                <LockIcon mr={2} />
                <Input type="password" placeholder="Enter your password" />
              </Flex>
            </FormControl>
            <Button colorScheme="teal" mt={6} width="100%">Login</Button>
          </GridItem>
        </Grid>

        {/* Footer */}
        <Box py={4} bg="white" color="teal" mt={4}>
          <Container maxW="container.lg">
            <Flex justifyContent="center">
              <Text>Â© 2024 Nixcel Software Pvt.Ltd All rights reserved.</Text>
            </Flex>
          </Container>
        </Box>
      </Box>
    </ChakraProvider>
  );
};

export default AdminLoginPage;
